    {
        "content": "<p>What is the difference between <code>wasmtime::Linker</code> and <code>wasmtime::component::Linker</code>?</p>\n<p><code>wasmtime_wasi::preview1::add_to_linker_async</code> expects a <code>wasmtime::Linker</code>, but <code>wasmtime_wasi_http::add_only_http_to_linker_async</code> expects a <code>wasmtime::component::Linker</code>. I'm not sure how to make these work together?</p>",
        "id": 482907199,
        "sender_full_name": "Lorenzo",
        "timestamp": 1731887887
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>wasmtime::Linker is for core wasm modules, while wasmtime::component::Linker is for wasm components.</p>",
        "id": 482965527,
        "sender_full_name": "bjorn3",
        "timestamp": 1731920791
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>wasip1 uses core wasm, while wasi-http is part of wasip2 which uses wasm components.</p>",
        "id": 482965671,
        "sender_full_name": "bjorn3",
        "timestamp": 1731920830
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>If you want to use wasi-http you will have to build your wasm module for wasip2 and use wasmtime_wasi::add_to_linker_async with a wasmtime::component::Linker.</p>",
        "id": 482965939,
        "sender_full_name": "bjorn3",
        "timestamp": 1731920910
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>For resources on what components are and what the component model is:</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://component-model.bytecodealliance.org/\">Component Model Book</a><br>\n<a href=\"https://github.com/WebAssembly/component-model/blob/main/design/mvp/Explainer.md\">CM explainer</a> (other good docs in there -- <a href=\"https://github.com/WebAssembly/component-model\">repo root</a> is worth looking at!)<br>\n<a href=\"https://github.com/WebAssembly/component-model/blob/main/design/mvp/WIT.md\">WebAssembly Interface Types (\"WIT\")</a></p>\n<div class=\"message_embed\"><a class=\"message_embed_image\" href=\"https://github.com/WebAssembly/component-model/blob/main/design/mvp/Explainer.md\" style=\"background-image: url(&quot;https://uploads.zulipusercontent.net/30a14fbfe675cc8e2f9dd61567b0aca93d4f7527/68747470733a2f2f6f70656e67726170682e6769746875626173736574732e636f6d2f326131326133383566666632656532393663653561396165363130636163333639336334663931313131373261386162306365343864323333653430353933372f576562417373656d626c792f636f6d706f6e656e742d6d6f64656c&quot;)\"></a><div class=\"data-container\"><div class=\"message_embed_title\"><a href=\"https://github.com/WebAssembly/component-model/blob/main/design/mvp/Explainer.md\" title=\"component-model/design/mvp/Explainer.md at main 路 WebAssembly/component-model\">component-model/design/mvp/Explainer.md at main 路 WebAssembly/component-model</a></div><div class=\"message_embed_description\">Repository for design and specification of the Component Model - WebAssembly/component-model</div></div></div><div class=\"message_embed\"><a class=\"message_embed_image\" href=\"https://github.com/WebAssembly/component-model\" style=\"background-image: url(&quot;https://uploads.zulipusercontent.net/30a14fbfe675cc8e2f9dd61567b0aca93d4f7527/68747470733a2f2f6f70656e67726170682e6769746875626173736574732e636f6d2f3261313261333835666666326565323936636535613961653631306361633336393363346639313131313732613861623063653438643233336534